{"lemma":"غُدَّةٌ","slug":"غُدَّةٌ","root":"غ.د.د","root_slug":"غ-د-د","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-د-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31478"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8F%D8%AF%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gland"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣud.da/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31478","headword_ar":"غُدَّةٌ","root":"gd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, S, O, L, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudadapN","text_ar":"غُدَدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, L, K) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A ganglion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any hard lump in the tendinous parts;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a lump of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flesh arising from disease, between the skin and the flesh, which may be made to move about:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any small nodous lump"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euqodap","text_ar":"عُقْدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the body"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O, L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O, L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surrounded by fat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O, L, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudadN","text_ar":"غُدَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[properly pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gud~apN","text_ar":"غُدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and also a coll. gen. n. of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudadapN","text_ar":"غُدَدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.]: (S, O, L, Msb, K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gud~apN","text_ar":"غُدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[is applied in the present day to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a ganglion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bubo:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wen:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and all these may be meant by its being said that it] also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swelling such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siloEap","text_ar":"سِلْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overspread by fat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gud~apN","text_ar":"غُدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies likewise The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plague,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pestilence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAEuwn","text_ar":"طَاعُون"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in camels;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, O, L, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadadN","text_ar":"غَدَدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"same in camels as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TAEwn","text_ar":"طاعون"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in man:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it attacks them in the groins, and seldom do they recover from it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is only in the belly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and when it extends to the camel's"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHor","text_ar":"نَحْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or part where he is stabbed, or stuck, when he is slaughtered], and to his groin, or arm-pit, the epithet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAbirN","text_ar":"دَابِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so in the TA, but in the O"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAriy^N","text_ar":"دَارِيٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which I believe to be the right reading,] is applied to him: so says IAar: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is also in the fat parts;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and between the flesh and the skin."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is between the fat and the hump"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of the camel]. (K.)       -A2-  Another signification of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gud~apN","text_ar":"غُدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of property; (L, K;) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi gud~apN mino maAlK","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ غُدَّةٌ مِنْ مَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He owes a part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion, of some property"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadaAy^idu","text_ar":"غَدَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,) and, in some of the copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gidaAdN","text_ar":"غِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And [these two pls.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadaAy^idu","text_ar":"غَدَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gidaAdN","text_ar":"غِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lots, portions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shares:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) thus, accord. to Fr, the former of them means in a verse of Lebeed cited and expl. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EadiydapN","text_ar":"عَدِيدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but the reading better known is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EadaAy^idu","text_ar":"عَدَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": accord. to Az,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadaAy^idu","text_ar":"غَدَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this instance signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"redundances."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)"}],"source_refs":["IDrd","S","O","L","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}